  Locus:
    Page: 65
    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Conscience
---
Conscience, as a mentor, the guide and compass of every act, leads ever to
happiness. When the individual can stay alone with his conscience and get
its approval, without knowing force or specious knowledge, then he begins
to know what real Happiness is.
